norbert smith : a life , also released as sir norbert smith : a life , is a 1989 mockumentary ( spoof documentary ) television film , charting the life and career of the fictitious british actor sir norbert smith . it stars harry &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in the title role . it was written by harry &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and geoffrey perkins and directed by geoff posner .